-- T. Rowe Price held 2.1 pct in Monte Paschi on June 16
-- By Elisa Anzolin
-- Tue Jun 24, 2014 05:20AM EDT
-- None



MILAN, June 24 (Reuters) - U.S. asset manager T. Rowe Price <TROW.O> held a 2.112 percent stake in Italian lender Banca Monte dei Paschi di Siena <BMPS.MI> on June 16, according to a filing published by Italian market regulator Consob on Tuesday.

